description: Enforces Pinia Setup Store pattern only. Option Stores are forbidden.
globs:
  - "src/stores/**/*.ts"
alwaysApply: true
---

# State Management Rules

Use only:

defineStore('id', () => {
  const state = ref(...)
  const computedValue = computed(...)
  function action() {}
  return { state, computedValue, action }
})

Do not use Option Stores.